{"tid":946644,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[自駕遊求評]四國十日遊","createTime":"2018-12-18T16:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T15:24:46.000Z","uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a59c31eac9570c637596bbd1d29b10bb4325b914","tid":946644,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:07:51.000Z","msg":"黎緊1月中同男朋友去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求評<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1: 2pm落機 － 高松空港<br />\n租車後直接去栗林公園，高松站個頭行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住高松<br />\n<br />\nDay 2: 朝早：屋島(聽講晏就去會曬到咩都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以要朝早）<br />\n小豆島<br />\n住高松<br />\n<br />\nDay 3: 由高松前往鳴門<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程1hr)</span><br />\n鳴門漩渦，鳴門公園<br />\n去德島市食飯＋周圍睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (唔打算上眉山）<br />\n由德島市前往大步危<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程1.5hr)</span><br />\n住大步危<br />\n<br />\nDay 4: 小步危，大步危，祖谷蔓橋，祖谷溫泉<br />\n前往四萬十<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程差唔多3粒鐘）</span>，途中可能係高知停一停，食個飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住四萬十<br />\n<br />\nDay 5: 玩四萬十，前往松山<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程2.5hr)</span>(我諗得返半日），下灘睇日落<br />\n住松山<br />\n<br />\nDay 6: 松山城，道後溫泉，玩松山市內<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住松山<br />\n<br />\nDay 7: 由松山前往大三島<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程1.5hr)</span>，再搭船去大久野島<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (應該搭13:35個班)<br />\n搭返去忠海，再去廣島<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程1個鐘多D）</span><br />\n住廣島<br />\n<br />\nDay 8: 玩廣島全日<br />\n住廣島<br />\n<br />\nDay 9: 前往尾道<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程1.5hr)</span>，玩尾道<br />\n再返高松<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程2hr)</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住高松<br />\n<br />\nDay 10: 朝早高松買下野，去機場返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 屋島應唔應該最後一日朝早先去／索性唔去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小豆島會唔會睇唔切d野？<br />\n2. 四萬十值唔值得特登去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 車程3粒鐘真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲未計去松山<br />\n如果唔去就直接大步危去松山<br />\n但唔去就只係去左一半四國<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 道後溫泉有人話伏，係咪真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4. 去埋廣島會唔會太chur?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔去廣島，應該會玩倉敷＋岡山<br />\n<br />\nThx!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cd60c7558baadc01d034c5a7f801ce07e009ff","tid":946644,"uid":225569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:28:18.000Z","msg":"四萬十川落去可以去足摺岬，足摺岬好正"},{"pid":"10cc29a6108c340cafe6d877407ddca4e3ff4cdc","tid":946644,"uid":35780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:40:01.000Z","msg":"太貪心"},{"pid":"c582012188a9f99c2b027c76c2f8b5b7024ecd16","tid":946644,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T18:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ac1ccec0337610ff51f8aca0e68b860f24110c","tid":946644,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10cc29a6108c340cafe6d877407ddca4e3ff4cdc","tid":946644,"uid":35780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:40:01.000Z","msg":"太貪心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T18:45:19.000Z","msg":"但係cut左廣島應該去邊好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發現10日四國真係唔多唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d048da23bc5416ff9b9712003587d0be947bbdd5","tid":946644,"uid":151341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T00:08:33.000Z","msg":"cut 左廣島啦，直島加小豆島有d 難控制時間，會去咩景點？"},{"pid":"5f097caef7b5f9bf1ca3545ee06d6c92361d4519","tid":946644,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d048da23bc5416ff9b9712003587d0be947bbdd5","tid":946644,"uid":151341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T00:08:33.000Z","msg":"cut 左廣島啦，直島加小豆島有d 難控制時間，會去咩景點？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:11:59.000Z","msg":"唔係直島 係屋島<br />\n係高松架<br />\n直島我上年去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過男朋友未去過<br />\n不過如果有時間我寧願去廣島<br />\n其實都係得原爆館同宮島<br />\n但係我好鐘意呢個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a79d935f4d88b0944fd29121e6507aae9e15bd","tid":946644,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:14:45.000Z","msg":"如果照去四萬十<br />\n唔去廣島，多出黎既時間只係去到岡山/倉敷<br />\n但係我去過覺得呢2個地方冇野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c80cf0bfb3856b7c658f9a4b3416637cf40464","tid":946644,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a61dd272978f1eaef7e29a4fb467e7754d25237","tid":946644,"uid":90767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f097caef7b5f9bf1ca3545ee06d6c92361d4519","tid":946644,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d048da23bc5416ff9b9712003587d0be947bbdd5","tid":946644,"uid":151341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T00:08:33.000Z","msg":"cut 左廣島啦，直島加小豆島有d 難控制時間，會去咩景點？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:11:59.000Z","msg":"唔係直島 係屋島<br />\n係高松架<br />\n直島我上年去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過男朋友未去過<br />\n不過如果有時間我寧願去廣島<br />\n其實都係得原爆館同宮島<br />\n但係我好鐘意呢個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:38:56.000Z","msg":"1日廣島好趕和 宮島又要等潮退 走都已經入夜<br />\n好難又去原爆又宮島"},{"pid":"77a0de94ee67951cbab9cacad14662b8bfa0dfca","tid":946644,"uid":39369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a59c31eac9570c637596bbd1d29b10bb4325b914","tid":946644,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:07:51.000Z","msg":"黎緊1月中同男朋友去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求評<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1: 2pm落機 － 高松空港<br />\n租車後直接去栗林公園，高松站個頭行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住高松<br />\n<br />\nDay 2: 朝早：屋島(聽講晏就去會曬到咩都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以要朝早）<br />\n小豆島<br />\n住高松<br />\n<br />\nDay 3: 由高松前往鳴門<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程1hr)</span><br />\n鳴門漩渦，鳴門公園<br />\n去德島市食飯＋周圍睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (唔打算上眉山）<br />\n由德島市前往大步危<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程1.5hr)</span><br />\n住大步危<br />\n<br />\nDay 4: 小步危，大步危，祖谷蔓橋，祖谷溫泉<br />\n前往四萬十<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程差唔多3粒鐘）</span>，途中可能係高知停一停，食個飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住四萬十<br />\n<br />\nDay 5: 玩四萬十，前往松山<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程2.5hr)</span>(我諗得返半日），下灘睇日落<br />\n住松山<br />\n<br />\nDay 6: 松山城，道後溫泉，玩松山市內<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住松山<br />\n<br />\nDay 7: 由松山前往大三島<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程1.5hr)</span>，再搭船去大久野島<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (應該搭13:35個班)<br />\n搭返去忠海，再去廣島<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程1個鐘多D）</span><br />\n住廣島<br />\n<br />\nDay 8: 玩廣島全日<br />\n住廣島<br />\n<br />\nDay 9: 前往尾道<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程1.5hr)</span>，玩尾道<br />\n再返高松<span style=\"color: red;\">(車程2hr)</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住高松<br />\n<br />\nDay 10: 朝早高松買下野，去機場返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 屋島應唔應該最後一日朝早先去／索性唔去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小豆島會唔會睇唔切d野？<br />\n2. 四萬十值唔值得特登去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 車程3粒鐘真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲未計去松山<br />\n如果唔去就直接大步危去松山<br />\n但唔去就只係去左一半四國<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 道後溫泉有人話伏，係咪真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4. 去埋廣島會唔會太chur?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔去廣島，應該會玩倉敷＋岡山<br />\n<br />\nThx!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:14:07.000Z","msg":"睇完覺得好CHUR<br />\n真心CUT左廣島，專心留係四國好過。<br />\n10日對四國黎講真係好少，我14日都唔夠玩。<br />\n<br />\n1. 小豆島都可以去到大半日，可以去到租單車，有時間順便可以去埋男女木島<br />\n2. 四萬十值去，真係好靚，你地有車既話可以去埋足摺岬，睇日落一流。<br />\n3. 道後溫泉其實都係一條大街，最特別係唔知6點定7點街口個大鐘有野睇。<br />\n    夜晚先去都會靚D，個到有埋餐廳食飯<br />\n4.  係好CHUR<br />\n<br />\n高松：金刀比羅宮<br />\n愛緩：今治踩單車(可以睇哂成個瀨戶內海)<br />\n高知： 足摺岬<br />\n上面呢D都推介你去<br />\n<br />\n我無記錯既話大步危去祖谷蔓橋好似都要40分鐘車程，來回都粒半鐘。<br />\n四國D野真係好早收工，尤其德島高知，冬天應該4點幾已經收緊鋪<br />\n同埋去高知記得去ひろめ市場食鰹のタタキ，好好食"},{"pid":"31811d9952d29ef748ab32e7f7226bea8245047e","tid":946644,"uid":195258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f097caef7b5f9bf1ca3545ee06d6c92361d4519","tid":946644,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d048da23bc5416ff9b9712003587d0be947bbdd5","tid":946644,"uid":151341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T00:08:33.000Z","msg":"cut 左廣島啦，直島加小豆島有d 難控制時間，會去咩景點？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:11:59.000Z","msg":"唔係直島 係屋島<br />\n係高松架<br />\n直島我上年去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過男朋友未去過<br />\n不過如果有時間我寧願去廣島<br />\n其實都係得原爆館同宮島<br />\n但係我好鐘意呢個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\